288
00:14:19,680 --> 00:14:21,080
I've been with Old Xuan for decades.

289
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:22,160
When have I ever enjoyed anything?

290
00:14:22,160 --> 00:14:23,320
Look at all of you,

291
00:14:23,400 --> 00:14:25,280
each one The Matriarch at home,

292
00:14:25,280 --> 00:14:26,600
whose word is law.

293
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:28,160
I've been envious for decades.

294
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:31,280
Xiu Mei,

295
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,280
Boss Man.

296
