304
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:48,560
When it comes to our industry,

305
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:51,040
Hongxing Factory is the real big brother.

306
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:52,600
Thank you, thank you, thank you.

307
00:14:52,920 --> 00:14:55,280
See, Old Xuan hasn't come yet.

308
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:57,480
