569
00:26:38,160 --> 00:26:41,560
isn't the old Deputy Director You Bingzhong.

570
00:26:41,760 --> 00:26:43,240
And today's Hongxing Factory

571
00:26:44,080 --> 00:26:46,360
isn't the Hongxing Factory of the past.

572
00:26:46,360 --> 00:26:47,800
You say you hold a grudge,

573
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:50,800
but against whom?

574
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:55,800
I don't hold any grudge.

575
00:26:56,440 --> 00:26:58,840
There's just one thing I can't forget.

576
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:02,920
Xiao Shi Quan

577
00:27:05,280 --> 00:27:07,920
had only been an apprentice for a year,

578
00:27:08,280 --> 00:27:11,400
and he insisted on being a Paper-making Master.

579
00:27:11,400 --> 00:27:11,920
I said,

580
00:27:12,560 --> 00:27:13,600
"Stop, stop.

581
00:27:13,600 --> 00:27:15,320
You're breaking the rules."

582
00:27:16,400 --> 00:27:17,640
And what did he say?

583
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:20,400
"What's the big deal?

584
00:27:20,600 --> 00:27:22,080
Paper-making Master, Curtain lifter, whatever.

585
00:27:23,080 --> 00:27:25,080
In the old days they were all just Paper beggars.

586
00:27:25,240 --> 00:27:26,000
You'd beg people to learn it,

587
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:27,400
and nobody would."

588
00:27:27,520 --> 00:27:28,560
Then he said to me,

589
00:27:28,560 --> 00:27:29,840
"What are you so smug about?"

590
00:27:31,560 --> 00:27:33,360
Those words have stuck with me.

591
00:27:34,240 --> 00:27:36,080
What kind of nonsense is that?

592
00:27:36,760 --> 00:27:37,720
Learning to make paper,

593
00:27:38,760 --> 00:27:41,920
and he didn't have the slightest bit of reverence.

594
00:27:42,320 --> 00:27:44,080
You tell me, shouldn't I have scolded him?

595
00:27:44,640 --> 00:27:45,960
Shouldn't I have made him stand as punishment?

596
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:46,320
You should have.

597
00:27:46,320 --> 00:27:47,880
By the old rules,

598
00:27:48,080 --> 00:27:49,920
an apprentice talking to his master like that

599
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:51,960
would get his mouth slapped raw.

600
00:27:53,440 --> 00:27:54,440
Exactly, exactly.

601
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:56,600
This whole thing,

602
00:27:56,760 --> 00:27:59,760
it was actually Deputy Director You Bingzhong

603
00:27:59,760 --> 00:28:00,680
who mishandled it.

604
00:28:07,120 --> 00:28:08,760
Xuan Yongnian! Xuan Yongnian!

605
00:28:08,760 --> 00:28:09,480
Get down here!

606
00:28:09,520 --> 00:28:10,760
Don't try to push us around!

607
00:28:10,760 --> 00:28:11,360
Xuan Yongnian! Xuan Yongnian!

608
00:28:11,840 --> 00:28:14,200
Comrades, everyone calm down.

609
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:15,520
Just hear me out, okay?

610
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:16,720
Everyone, please calm down.

611
00:28:16,720 --> 00:28:17,760
Just listen to me.

612
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:20,000
I'm You Bingzhong, our deputy factory head.

613
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:21,360
