619
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:29,200
Does that deserve punishment?

620
00:28:29,200 --> 00:28:30,520
Exactly! Exactly! Exactly!

621
00:28:30,520 --> 00:28:33,200
Which rule did Xuan Yongnian follow

622
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:35,040
