625
00:28:39,240 --> 00:28:39,840
Yes!

626
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:41,240
Xuan Yongnian!

627
00:28:41,600 --> 00:28:42,640
Xuan Yongnian, get out here!

628
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:43,680
