637
00:28:54,440 --> 00:28:55,400
What's my problem?

638
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:56,920
What's my problem?

639
00:28:57,560 --> 00:28:58,840
What problem don't you have?

640
00:28:59,040 --> 00:29:00,840
