650
00:29:12,320 --> 00:29:13,560
Right now, immediately!

651
00:29:13,720 --> 00:29:15,040
Apologize! Apologize! Apologize!

652
00:29:15,040 --> 00:29:17,360
He must apologize! He must apologize!

653
00:29:17,360 --> 00:29:21,640
Apologize! Apologize! You must apologize!

654
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:24,040
Xuan Yongnian, apologize right now!

655
00:29:24,040 --> 00:29:26,680
Apologize! You must apologize! Apologize!

656
00:29:27,720 --> 00:29:29,680
Xuan Yongnian! Xuan Yongnian!

657
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:31,200
You want me, the master,

658
00:29:31,200 --> 00:29:32,880
