665
00:29:56,360 --> 00:29:58,720
Why can't you let it go?

666
00:30:01,960 --> 00:30:03,840
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

667
00:30:04,560 --> 00:30:06,320
I, Xuan Yongnian, am petty.

668
00:30:06,320 --> 00:30:07,480
I can't let it go.

669
00:30:08,120 --> 00:30:09,280
I can't let it go.

670
00:30:10,520 --> 00:30:11,680
I can't let it go!

671
00:30:14,320 --> 00:30:14,800
Hey, wait...

672
00:30:15,200 --> 00:30:15,800
Old Xuan.

673
00:30:16,280 --> 00:30:17,080
Old Xuan!

674
00:30:19,280 --> 00:30:20,040
Your coat.

675
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:22,000
Come on, don't catch a cold.

676
00:30:42,560 --> 00:30:43,360
Senior brother

677
00:30:47,040 --> 00:30:47,840
Senior brother

678
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:51,000
