721
00:33:32,640 --> 00:33:34,120
and a Curtain lifter.

722
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:39,120
I've been the Xuans' Curtain lifter.

723
00:33:39,560 --> 00:33:42,240
I put in more effort, yielded more,

724
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:44,840
