733
00:34:16,560 --> 00:34:19,239
Ever since she said those words to me,

734
00:34:19,760 --> 00:34:21,159
I understood.

735
00:34:23,000 --> 00:34:24,360
For our family

736
00:34:24,639 --> 00:34:26,400
to live well,

737
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:27,960
for my whole life,

738
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:31,280
I've got to lift that curtain

739
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:34,080
