740
00:34:36,719 --> 00:34:38,239
Of course, of course.

741
00:34:46,719 --> 00:34:47,520
Come on.

742
00:34:49,639 --> 00:34:50,440
Let's go.

743
00:34:50,679 --> 00:34:51,639
Let's go home.

744
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:58,080
