751
00:35:14,920 --> 00:35:15,800
Coming, coming.

752
00:35:16,400 --> 00:35:18,120
Everyone, please make way.

753
00:35:18,120 --> 00:35:18,560
Excuse me.

754
00:35:18,560 --> 00:35:20,080
Watch the cart, watch the cart.

755
00:35:20,080 --> 00:35:20,880
Come, come, come.

756
00:35:21,160 --> 00:35:21,600
Watch the cart.

757
00:35:21,600 --> 00:35:22,360
