853
00:39:06,560 --> 00:39:07,760
is that money

854
00:39:09,120 --> 00:39:10,560
just blown in by the wind?

855
00:39:10,640 --> 00:39:11,960
Are we just getting old?

856
00:39:12,080 --> 00:39:14,280
Even if I'm old, I wouldn't want his thing.

857
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:18,040
I remember making one out of paper pulp as a kid,

858
00:39:18,560 --> 00:39:19,560
a little horse cart.

859
00:39:19,680 --> 00:39:22,200
Give it a push and it'd rattle forward.

860
00:39:22,560 --> 00:39:23,560
Pretty nice.

861
00:39:24,520 --> 00:39:25,760
Never mind selling it,

862
00:39:26,240 --> 00:39:28,760
my dad nearly beat me to death for it.

863
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:30,880
Now I'm thinking,

864
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:32,720
wasn't my little horse cart

865
00:39:33,400 --> 00:39:35,280
better than his thingamajig?

866
00:39:35,280 --> 00:39:36,960
I never saw your little horse cart,

867
00:39:37,400 --> 00:39:38,440
so I can't really say.

868
00:39:39,800 --> 00:39:41,040
But I feel,

869
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:43,760
when it comes to making paper,

870
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:45,320
your son can't match you.

871
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,680
But when it comes to cultural creative goods,

872
00:39:47,200 --> 00:39:48,760
you'd better learn

873
00:39:49,120 --> 00:39:50,320
a thing or two from your son.

874
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:57,920
Where are you going?

875
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:01,040
I'm going to learn from him.

876
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:02,360
I want to learn his tricks.

877
00:40:02,360 --> 00:40:03,840
What have I become?

878
00:40:05,920 --> 00:40:06,920
You don't want this anymore?

879
00:40:07,760 --> 00:40:08,920
Keep it for fun.

880
00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:10,960
I'll keep it for fun.

881
00:40:13,680 --> 00:40:14,920
Just a few days left.

882
00:40:14,920 --> 00:40:16,240
Everyone, hang in there.

883
00:40:16,600 --> 00:40:17,640
Persistence to the end is victory.

884
00:40:17,640 --> 00:40:18,520
Don't let your guard down.

885
00:40:18,520 --> 00:40:19,240
Did you hear me?

886
00:40:19,240 --> 00:40:20,040
Absolutely, got it.

887
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:21,600
By the way, Wang Hao.

888
00:40:21,800 --> 00:40:23,440
Out-of-town vendors are heading back this afternoon.

889
00:40:23,440 --> 00:40:25,000
Please arrange it for them.

890
00:40:25,320 --> 00:40:26,400
It's all arranged.

891
00:40:26,560 --> 00:40:27,520
Starting at three-thirty.

892
00:40:27,520 --> 00:40:28,600
Four buses.

893
00:40:28,600 --> 00:40:30,720
Shuttling between the market and the train station.

894
00:40:31,600 --> 00:40:32,400
And then?

895
00:40:32,680 --> 00:40:33,800
What about the sanitation workers?

896
00:40:33,800 --> 00:40:35,120
I've confirmed that as well.

897
00:40:35,480 --> 00:40:37,640
The conference ends at five.

898
00:40:37,640 --> 00:40:39,160
People start leaving at five-thirty.

899
00:40:39,160 --> 00:40:40,720
Sanitation workers come in at six-thirty.

900
00:40:40,720 --> 00:40:41,920
Then they start cleaning.

901
00:40:41,920 --> 00:40:44,000
By the next morning, everyone gets back

902
00:40:44,160 --> 00:40:47,040
a tidy and spotless venue.

903
00:40:47,440 --> 00:40:48,880
Wow, you guys are impressive!

904
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:51,840
Sharp eyes and clear minds.

905
00:40:51,840 --> 00:40:53,080
And steady hands too.

906
00:40:53,560 --> 00:40:55,480
Our team has really been well trained.

907
00:40:55,480 --> 00:40:56,720
Absolutely.

908
00:40:56,720 --> 00:40:59,440
Our teamwork is so seamless,

909
00:40:59,600 --> 00:41:01,000
let's work together again next time.

910
00:41:01,320 --> 00:41:02,120
Sure.

911
00:41:02,320 --> 00:41:03,120
Come on.

912
00:41:04,200 --> 00:41:05,640
Just hang in there for a few more days.

913
00:41:05,640 --> 00:41:07,800
I'll treat everyone to a big meal soon.

914
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:08,440
Come on.

915
00:41:08,680 --> 00:41:09,560
Let's go!

916
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:11,080
Let me check.

917
00:41:11,080 --> 00:41:11,800
Time's up.

918
00:41:11,800 --> 00:41:13,000
Hurry, go open the venue.

919
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:13,400
Quick, quick, quick!

920
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:13,760
Okay, okay, okay.

921
00:41:13,760 --> 00:41:14,560
Let's go, let's go, let's go.

922
00:41:14,560 --> 00:41:15,360
Hurry up.

923
00:41:20,920 --> 00:41:21,320
Wait

924
00:41:21,320 --> 00:41:24,000
A big boss like you, riding a tricycle?

925
00:41:24,080 --> 00:41:24,760
Director Lin

926
00:41:24,760 --> 00:41:26,000
Don't tease me.

927
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:27,240
I'm delivering goods to a client.

928
00:41:27,400 --> 00:41:28,680
So, are you making money?

929
00:41:29,160 --> 00:41:30,000
Not bad, not bad

930
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:31,120
What do you mean "not bad"?

931
00:41:31,120 --> 00:41:31,840
Did you make money or not?

932
00:41:31,840 --> 00:41:33,760
Just signed 60-70k in cultural products.

933
00:41:33,920 --> 00:41:35,400
Compared to President Xiao's group,

934
00:41:35,400 --> 00:41:36,200
It's nothing.

935
00:41:36,880 --> 00:41:37,760
The key thing is,

936
00:41:37,800 --> 00:41:39,000
I met a few new clients.

937
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:40,400
That's already a lot.

938
00:41:40,400 --> 00:41:42,360
Just keep up the quality and service

939
00:41:42,360 --> 00:41:42,920
Stay honest

940
00:41:42,920 --> 00:41:44,280
and you'll keep the clients

941
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:46,800
Director Lin

942
00:41:47,000 --> 00:41:48,640
You're making me embarrassed

943
00:41:48,840 --> 00:41:50,000
I owe you an apology

944
00:41:50,520 --> 00:41:51,280
A guy like me

945
00:41:51,280 --> 00:41:53,360
I usually just keep my head down chasing money

946
00:41:53,480 --> 00:41:55,040
Never looked up to see people clearly

947
00:41:55,800 --> 00:41:57,240
Please don't hold it against me

948
00:41:58,200 --> 00:41:59,000
You know, people

949
00:41:59,000 --> 00:42:00,040
you gotta savor slowly

950
00:42:00,480 --> 00:42:02,000
And I've figured you out, Director Lin.

951
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:03,680
You're top-notch.

952
00:42:04,440 --> 00:42:05,600
Give it time

953
00:42:05,600 --> 00:42:07,480
and you'll see what kind of man Er Hu is

954
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:09,360
Okay, I'll savor it slowly

955
00:42:09,800 --> 00:42:10,520
Go get back to work

956
00:42:10,520 --> 00:42:11,240
I'm off

957
00:42:12,280 --> 00:42:13,160
Take it easy

958
00:42:16,880 --> 00:42:18,680
Weather's great today

959
00:42:19,040 --> 00:42:19,840
Nice day

960
00:42:19,840 --> 00:42:20,600
Really nice

961
00:42:21,640 --> 00:42:23,800
This Lin Yiran is out of line.

962
00:42:23,800 --> 00:42:25,040
The leaders will be here any minute

963
00:42:25,040 --> 00:42:26,920
She didn't even clear the crowd out.

964
00:42:26,920 --> 00:42:27,800
It's a mess

965
00:42:27,800 --> 00:42:29,040
Why should we clear them out?

966
00:42:30,160 --> 00:42:31,160
It's great

967
00:42:31,560 --> 00:42:33,240
Young people, wonderful

968
00:42:33,320 --> 00:42:35,360
We host this Four Treasures of the Study

969
00:42:35,360 --> 00:42:37,360
event for exactly this kind of crowd.

970
00:42:37,360 --> 00:42:37,920
Right

971
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:38,880
Well organized

972
00:42:39,960 --> 00:42:41,000
I just thought it looked messy.

973
00:42:41,000 --> 00:42:42,480
Worried the leaders would be annoyed

974
00:42:46,680 --> 00:42:48,280
Who changed this sign?

975
00:42:48,400 --> 00:42:49,040
I did

976
00:42:49,040 --> 00:42:50,320
How's it look? Pretty good, right?

977
00:42:51,280 --> 00:42:52,080
Take it down

978
00:42:52,800 --> 00:42:53,440
Right now

979
00:42:53,440 --> 00:42:54,800
What are you up to?

980
00:42:54,920 --> 00:42:55,720
Take it down immediately

981
00:42:56,480 --> 00:42:57,120
Secretary Peng

982
00:42:57,200 --> 00:42:58,240
The leaders' car is here.
